name: openchat
description: A family of open-source models trained on a wide variety of data, surpassing ChatGPT on various benchmarks. Updated to version 3.5-0106.
readme_html:
OpenChat is set of open-source language models, fine-tuned with C-RLFT: a strategy inspired by offline reinforcement learning.

Updated to OpenChat-3.5-1210, this new version of the model model excels at coding tasks and scores very high on many open-source LLM benchmarks.
